query:
SELECT c.id, c.concert_date, a.name as artist, v.name as venue 
FROM concerts c 
JOIN artists a ON c.artist_id = a.id 
JOIN venues v ON c.venue_id = v.id 
WHERE a.name LIKE '%Slaughter Beach%' 
ORDER BY c.concert_date;
